---
const values = [
  {
    title: "Private movement, clear timing",
    description: "Every pickup, drop-off, and tour route is arranged around guest timing, luggage, destination flow, and comfortable private travel.",
  },
  {
    title: "Bintan routes handled locally",
    description: "From ferry terminals and airport movement to Lagoi, Trikora, Tanjung Pinang, and activity stops, the service is shaped around real Bintan travel needs.",
  },
  {
    title: "Easy WhatsApp confirmation",
    description: "Guests can share date, pickup point, guest count, route ideas, and special requests before confirming availability and the best vehicle option.",
  },
];
---

<section class="editorial-section-dark">
  <div class="editorial-container">
    <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="editorial-kicker">Our positioning</p>
        <h2 class="editorial-title mt-3 text-[#f8fafc]">
          Bintan Prestige is built for guests who want the trip handled calmly.
        </h2>
        <p class="editorial-lede mt-5 text-slate-400">
          The service focuses on private taxi, transfer, and tour coordination across Bintan. It keeps planning direct and human, so guests can move from arrival to resort, beach, city stop, or activity without a complicated booking flow.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-400">
          Instead of a generic transport listing, Bintan Prestige presents a premium route partner: clear communication, practical local suggestions, and driver-supported travel for couples, families, groups, and corporate guests.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-4">
        {values.map((item) => (
          <article class="editorial-card rounded-[8px] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[#f8e7a1]/34">
            <h3 class="font-[var(--font-editorial-heading)] text-2xl font-medium leading-tight text-[#f8fafc]">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">{item.description}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
